so i think i've updated the lj once since ive been here but here it goes:
first off-GOOD WORK CALIFORNIA. despite what mary catherine thinks, this is the direction we need to be going in, and i for one am happy we will be paying less taxes-i don't understand why one wouldn't be happy.
i have my first test today-in 40 min-in econ-hopefully i'll do ok:)
school is good-i went home last weekend and i saw my bubba!! oh how i miss him.
but it can get pretty boring here on the weekends-now i can see why college students drink so much.
but i have class with paker today-for those of you who don't know he is te absolutely beautiful mormon football quarterback in my seminar class and it really makes my day
me and the roomie are haing a little "tif" right now-so to make matter worse i have taken te dvd player to yodit's room and when i am in the room i blast country music! but there are some great songs-if u still dl music dl mark wills remember me-i cry and cry and cry when i hear it
to micahel and mary-catherine-NOVEMBER 1st!! i cannot wait!! i miss you guys so much and can't wait to see you-maybe if jamie you wanted to a little road trip on ur bday come too!!!:)  i cannot wait till thanksgiving when we can all be together again-not many people here appreciate the humor we have-i just think they don't understand it!
i think thats all thats new: we're having a recall party tonight and my friend veronica's bf is coming up 2morrow so i tihnk we're gonna go to a bar in frisco
ok i love you all!
people send me mail! i wanna see picturs-ERIN SEARS IF I DO NOT GET SENT HOMECOMING PICTURES OF YOU, I THINK YOU WILL DIE-and the same goes for te rest of the seniors at the nade!
i never get any mail unless its from safeway-its so sad, the bank doesnt even send me mail:(
here's the address in case u lost it: 
po box 3238 moraga ca 94575

love you all!!
